situation: My wife of 6 years decided one day last week she wanted to end things.  This comes after finding out

final_result.label: normal
final_result.response: That makes sense. It can be hard to know what someone else wants, especially in such a tough situation. Have you thought about asking her directly what her feelings are regarding the future and family? It could help to get her perspective and bring you both a bit closer together during this time.
